{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"39abb6e7d3","title":"丽江县革命委员会关于教师集中搞“一打三反”运动有关补助问题的通知","origin":"根据档案材料翻印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ed123c0680","index":0,"year":1970,"month":8,"day":16,"articleId":"39abb6e7d3"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b6d8a885e","name":"革命委员会","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"2e99ca34d1","name":"一打三反","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ce66022e17","type":"title","text":"丽江县革命委员会关于教师集中搞“一打三反”运动有关补助问题的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39abb6e7d3"},{"id":"1b9ee7a88e","type":"subtitle","text":"最高指示","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39abb6e7d3"},{"id":"8f3cff0a1c","type":"paragraph","text":"财政的支出，应该根据节省的方针","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39abb6e7d3"},{"id":"dc0a879c15","type":"paragraph","text":"这次全县教师分别集中在各公社搞运动，在运动期间，有关公杂费、伙食补助问题，经县革委会常委会研究提出以下补助办法：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39abb6e7d3"},{"id":"e14d8513c2","type":"paragraph","text":"一、公杂费按参加运动的实有人数计算，每人每天五分。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39abb6e7d3"},{"id":"dc463ab4bb","type":"paragraph","text":"二、补助伙食费的问题，分别四种情况：","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39abb6e7d3"},{"id":"511d899a49","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）贫下中农代表参加运动的，除交够粮食一斤外，每人每天补助伙食费三角。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39abb6e7d3"},{"id":"f8fdb230e6","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）民办公助的教师，领取10元以下的，每人每天补助伙食费二角。领取15元以下的每人每天补助一角。民办无补助费的，每人每天补助伙食费三角。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39abb6e7d3"},{"id":"5ef4a60f47","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）炊事员按30人顾一人计算，工资30元，伙食自付。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39abb6e7d3"},{"id":"4d273a8bf9","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）公办教师，一律不补助伙食费。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39abb6e7d3"},{"id":"45d6a911fe","type":"paragraph","text":"三、肉食补助，按参加运动的实有人数算，每人每天补助一两。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39abb6e7d3"},{"id":"53f31d4f2d","type":"paragraph","text":"四、车费按时规定报销，没有住勤费。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39abb6e7d3"},{"id":"a583588032","type":"paragraph","text":"五、民办教师、贫下中农代表口粮，按每天交足定量外，不足部分根据情况给予部分补助。每天每人不得超过一斤的标准。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39abb6e7d3"},{"id":"6c73768027","type":"paragraph","text":"以上补助办法，从八月十五日电话会议通知之日起执行。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39abb6e7d3"},{"id":"c1ca7403cc","type":"paragraph","text":" 丽江县革委会政工组丽江县革委会办公室一九七O年八月十六日","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39abb6e7d3"},{"id":"352ccb093b","type":"paragraph","text":"发：四大组、县属各站、各公社、供销社、粮管所。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39abb6e7d3"}],"page":{"id":"3ee9e2a4cb","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"39abb6e7d3","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}